  "sections": {
    "Background": {
      "text": "Reverse Bennett: fracture of fifth metacarpal base, with extensor carpi ulnaris traction on distal metacarpal while proximal fragment still algined with carpals\nSee\nThumb fracture\nfor Bennett fracture",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
